Package session.frontend

sessiondvd contains set of classes to manage different sessions and their functionalities for DVD Rental System.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
iSession Provides all the functionalities of a DVD rental system.
pSession Provides privileged-operations interface for a DVD Rental System.
sSession Provides standard operations interface for DVD Rental System.
 

Class Summary
AdminSession Class provides access to privileged commands through pSession interface.
SessionErrors This class stores all the generic errors that may occur during a particular session.
SessionManager This class acts as a MEDIATOR to manage the ADMIN and STANDARD sessions.
StandardSession This class contains all functionality that is command between ADMIN and STANDARD sessions.
 

Enum Summary
SessionType Type of sessions within DVD Rental System.
 

Package session.frontend Description

sessiondvd contains set of classes to manage different sessions and their functionalities for DVD Rental System.
